Enum PaymentResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PaymentResults>
      • com.symbol.emdk.payment.PaymentResults
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<PaymentResults>

    public enum PaymentResults
extends Enum<PaymentResults>
    Defines all the error codes the payment API returns.
